itemDescription: Welsh royal Princess; daughter of Llywelyn II

wikipedia_page.main: Gwenllian of Wales or Gwenllian ferch Llywelyn (June 1282 – 7 June 1337) was the only child of Llywelyn ap Gruffudd, the last native Prince of Wales (Welsh: Tywysog Cymru). She is sometimes confused with Gwenllian ferch Gruffudd, who lived two centuries earlier.
